We will now start the test portion. In this experiment you will see a row of letters. If the middle letter is H, please press the H Key. If the middle letter is F, press the F Key. Respond as quickly and accurately as possible. Ignore the letters not in the middle!

On some trials, you will see a star appear with or shortly after the letters. Do not respond if you see a star. Do not slow down your responses to the letter in order to wait for the star.

Press Enter to continue.
